game.name: Frozen Anna Dog Care
game.description:
Your favorite Anna is blessed with two cute dog pets. She usually plays with them and has fun during her free time. One day her pets were injured when she was enjoying her free time with them. Now they are crying with pain. Will you come forward to help the girl to take care of her pets? Join Frozen Anna Dog Care game and prove the world that you are also concerned for the animals! Follow the instructions properly to complete each task successfully!
Give them the immediate medical treatment and then provide them a proper bath in this brand new animal game! You also have to dress them up one by one with the help of cute clothes. Choose the dog first and then get ready to make a surgery, take a shower and dress it up! Use the towel first to clean up your chosen dog and then give him the needful medicine and get his injury treated with the bandage! Now give him a proper bath using the soap, shampoo and water. Do not forget to leave the ball in the tub to make him play in this html5 girls game. 
Your next job then is to dress him up with the cool outfits so that it can play with Anna with full of confidence. Follow the same instructions for the second pet and help princess to have lots of fun with her lovely dogs! It is up to you to use the medical tools to treat her dogs and make them healthy. Remove all the mess first before taking any further step for their care! Good luck to try out more animal games for free, no download required!
